    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 10 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>diced courgette</strong></p><p>Top the courgette with your <strong>basa fillet[s] </strong>and press the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs </strong>onto the fish</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 12-15 min further or until the breadcrumbs are crisp and golden and the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>Provençal-style crumbed basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
