    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(don't like raw garlic? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong> to a small bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your<strong> garlic & parsley oil</strong></p>",
